Package GameView

Class card

java.lang.Object
java.awt.Component
java.awt.Container
javax.swing.JComponent
javax.swing.JPanel
GameView.card
All Implemented Interfaces:
cardInterface, unoConstants, java.awt.image.ImageObserver, java.awt.MenuContainer, java.io.Serializable, javax.accessibility.Accessible
Direct Known Subclasses:
actionCard, numCard, wildCard
public abstract class card
extends javax.swing.JPanel
implements cardInterface, unoConstants
The card class is serves as the base card class and is used to create a UNO card object. The object will represent the color, number, and action of each card.
